There's two problems:

* TestConvertStructTypes.test_from_numpy_large is being run even though it should be disabled by {{pytest.mark.large_memory}}. This seems like a regression in pytest
* That test fails -- it hits the following DCHECK in arrow/python/numpy_to_arrow.cc:315

{code}
  DCHECK_NE(dtype_->type_num, NPY_OBJECT)
      << "This class does not handle NPY_OBJECT arrays";
{code}

I opened ARROW-4181
